puts '<?xml version="1.0"?>' puts '<items>' list.each_line do |l| name, url = l.chomp.split("\t") query = "{query}".downcase next unless name.downcase.include?(query) || url.downcase.include?(query)
puts(<<-EOC) <item arg="#{url}" autocomplete="#{name}"> <title>#{name}</title> <subtitle>#{url}</subtitle> </item> EOC end puts '</items>'
